From: Cromite Developer <developer@cromite.org>
Date: Tue, 06 Jan 2026 12:00:00 +0000
Subject: Add AdGuard DNS provider with all variants

Add AdGuard DNS as a built-in DoH provider with three variants:
- Default (with ad blocking and tracker protection)
- Family Protection (blocks adult content + ads)
- Unfiltered (no filtering)

All variants include proper privacy policy links and are displayed globally.

License: GPL-2.0-or-later
---
 net/dns/public/doh_provider_entry.cc | 36 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 36 insertions(+)

diff --git a/net/dns/public/doh_provider_entry.cc b/net/dns/public/doh_provider_entry.cc
index 1234567..abcdefg 100644
--- a/net/dns/public/doh_provider_entry.cc
+++ b/net/dns/public/doh_provider_entry.cc
@@ -150,6 +150,42 @@ const DohProviderEntry::List& DohProviderEntry::GetList() {
         /*display_countries=*/{},
         LoggingLevel::kNormal),
 
+    // AdGuard DNS Default - Blocks ads, trackers, and malicious domains
+    DohProviderEntry(
+        "AdGuardDefault",
+        feature_list,
+        /*ip_addresses=*/
